http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Power-supply-to-be-disrupted-today/article14015243.ece

Electricity supply to areas including Palayam police quarters and Chandrasekharan Nair Stadium, coming under the Cantonment electrical section, will be disrupted from 9 a.m. to 5 p.m. on Saturday.According to an official release issued here on Friday, power supply will also be affected in areas including Jagathy bund road, coming under the Poojappura electrical section, and Kattaikonam, Vazhayila, Karoor and Thettichira, coming under the Pothencode electrical section, on Saturday.These will be due to maintenance works undertaken by the Kerala State Electricity Board.